trans-unit.source: Provides the event data for creating fast <see cref="Overload:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent" /> overloads by using the <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore(System.Int32,System.Int32,System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.EventData*)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: 藉由使用 <see cref="Overload:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent" /> 方法，為快速建立 <see cref="M:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEventCore(System.Int32,System.Int32,System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.EventData*)" /> 多載提供事件資料。

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.EventData> structure.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何使用<xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.EventData>結構。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the pointer to the data for the new <see cref="Overload:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent" /> overload.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定新 <see cref="Overload:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent" /> 多載的資料指標。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of payload items in the new <see cref="Overload:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent" /> overload.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定新的 <see cref="Overload:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource.WriteEvent" /> 多載中的承載項目數目。

trans-unit.source: The number of payload items in the new overload.
trans-unit.target: 新多載中的裝載項目數目。
